‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ app.js
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Dockerfile

4Ô∏è‚É£ Build & Run the To-Do App in Docker

From inside the todo-app directory:

docker build -t todo-app .

docker run -d -p 3000:3000 todo-app


Now open in browser:

üëâ http://localhost:3000
